Alert: Get tested immediately and self-isolate for 14 days
HealthAdviceHTML:
Anyone who was in the Grange Buffet for over an hour is a close contact and must immediately get tested and self-isolate for 14 days regardless of the result.

Anyone who was in the Grange Buffet for less than an hour is a casual contact and must get tested and self-isolate until they receive a negative result. You should continue to monitor for symptoms and if any symptoms occur, get tested again.

Anyone who was at the Workers Sports Club (but not in the Grange Buffet) should monitor for symptoms and if they occur get tested immediately and self-isolate until you receive a negative result.
